comments.body: From here: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=5096261.0Original price: Gifted with several 2017 Kialara Silver Series - To The Moon piecesMaterials: .999 Silver 1oz coinDenomination: NoneMintage: 117/130*Artist: Maxfield MellenbruchKnown errors: None* On 10/16/2017 Max uploaded a post in the To The Moon production update blog saying that he has acquired 117 Error coins. In a later post, uploaded on 12/19/2017, he speaks of 130 error coins.The blog post referenced in that link is apparently now gone, but the error itself is stated on https://wiki.coin.community/Kialara_Silver_Series_2017_%E2%80%93_%E2%80%98To_the_Moon%E2%80%99#Error_Coins"During minting some of the silver coins were created with the wrong back design.
